  "title": "Sales Product Advisor (Part/Full Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Salary range: </strong></p><p><strong>Full time: Basic SGD$1,500 - SGD$3,000+\n(depending on experience), including generous commission</strong></p><p><br /><strong>Job Highlights:</strong></p><p>Positive and collaborative working environment</p><p>Generous commission</p><p>Performance bonus</p><p>Staff discounts</p><p>Medical benefits</p><p>Training provided</p><p><br /><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>·       Promote and sell company products to achieve sales targets</p><p>·       Conduct health events at assigned retail locations,\nincluding setting up and dismantling of roadshows if any</p><p>·       Project positive image of the company and the brand\n(e.g. ensure product displays are well presented with proper and correct\nsignages in prominent locations)</p><p>·       Provide sales feedback and suggestions to Sales Executive/Manager.</p><p>·       Carry out any other duties as and when assigned by Sales\nExecutive/Manager.</p><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>·       Minimum pass in Secondary Education.</p><p>·       Working experience in Sales/Promotion and excellent\nproduct demonstration skills will be preferred</p><p>·       Proactive/self-disciplined/keen to learn and\npossess a strong team spirit</p><p>·       As we are selling Traditional Chinese Proprietary\nMedicines, as defined by HSA, our customer base is naturally more Chinese\nbased. Therefore, proficiency in Mandarin and other Chinese dialects is\nbeneficial</p><p>·       Work during retail hours (may be PH or weekends)</p><p>·       Interest in health-related topics are ideal</p><p><br /><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><p>·       Basic with high commission, transport claims\nallowed for company sales events</p><p>·       Retail hours and multi-location on rotational basis</p><p>·       6-day work week, 7-hour workday</p><p>·       Part time positions available (4-day work week)</p><p>If interested, kindly send\nus your resume and contact us at:</p><p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:enquiry.sg@thomsonhealth.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">enquiry.sg@thomsonhealth.com</a></p><p>Website: <a href=\"https://sg.thomsonhealth.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://sg.thomsonhealth.com/</a><u></u></p>",
